  "feesApplyText": "A brand new contemporary 2 bed apartment set in a beautiful development by London Square, located within 5 minutes of walk from Caledonian Road Station (Piccadilly Line), in the heart of North London.  King's Cross station is one stop away offering London's best transport links nationally and internationally.The 5th floor property benefits from a large open plankitchen/reception room with floor to ceilings windows and direct access onto a private terrace. Further benefits include two double bedrooms (master with en-suite and built-in wardrobe) and a luxury family bathroom. Residents can enjoy a 24hr concierge, a gym and communal courtyard gardens.  This property provides easy access to the City, West End, King's Cross, Camden and Islington.  It is also very convenient to students who attend some of the leading universities in the capital, including Central Saint Martins, UCL, London Metropolitan University, City University of London,  University of Arts London and others.",
